dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's extremely heartbreaking, it's not ideal.\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will be heading back to Brisbane, having a chat with the surgeon, we will just see where we go from there.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\", \"score\": 0.4727035960912667, \"rank\": 0.5594542848925047, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not entirely sure what the recovery process looks like moving forward but I have got an amazing team around me, and (I am) trying to be as positive as possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old played a crucial role in helping the Australian Women's Artistic Gymnastics team earn a spot in the 2024 Olympics through last year's world championships.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9995540760112047, \"rank\": 0.00017645188499386402, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9663151317379987, \"rank\": 0.0347965084921175, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking to Instagram after the team qualified in October, Godwin said: \\\"The Aussie WAG team are going to the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1370